data.description: SPREAD OUT IN THIS PRE-CERTIFIED HOME! Home inspection done & home warranty included! This TWO STORY STUNNER is located in the alluring Cedarhurst Subdivision and is within a mile of the elementary, middle, and high schools. It features a large living room with TONS of natural light and a gas fireplace, a roomy kitchen with an big island, SS appliances, and a formal dining area. The 1st floor also includes your laundry room and half bath. Upstairs, discover a primary bedroom with its ensuite and dual closets, three more large bedrooms, and another full bath. The full LL is open-concept and ready for your touch. With an attached 2.5-car insulated garage, a new deck off the back, six panel doors, & maintenance-free exterior you'll instantly fall in love! 48hr min bind, no bind on wekends/hol
